  <h1>Basic Form</h1>
  <p class="lead">Accessible form pattern using the form-field custom element. Native HTML5 validation with CSS-only feedback states.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>This snippet provides a complete contact form with all common input types. It uses the <code>&lt;form-field&gt;</code> custom element for consistent styling and the <code>&lt;layout-stack&gt;</code> element for vertical spacing.</p>
      <p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Native HTML5 validation (no JavaScript required)</li>
        <li>Accessible labels and helper text</li>
        <li>Consistent field styling via <code>&lt;form-field&gt;</code></li>
        <li>Proper autocomplete attributes</li>
        <li>Checkbox and radio group patterns</li>
        <li>Form actions with reset and submit</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Live Example</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>A contact form with text inputs, select, textarea, checkbox, and radio buttons.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/form-basic.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/form-basic"
      title="Contact Form"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Source Code</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>The form-field element wraps each input with its label and helper text.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <code-block language="html" label="form-basic.html">&lt;form action="/submit" method="POST"&gt;
  &lt;layout-stack data-layout-gap="l"&gt;
    &lt;h2&gt;Contact Form&lt;/h2&gt;

    &lt;!-- Text input with required validation --&gt;
    &lt;form-field&gt;
      &lt;label for="name"&gt;Full Name&lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;input
        type="text"
        id="name"
        name="name"
        required
        autocomplete="name"
        placeholder="John Doe"
        aria-describedby="name-msg"
      &gt;
      &lt;output id="name-msg" for="name" aria-live="polite"&gt;
        Enter your full name as it appears on official documents.
      &lt;/output&gt;
    &lt;/form-field&gt;

    &lt;!-- Email input with type validation --&gt;
    &lt;form-field&gt;
      &lt;label for="email"&gt;Email Address&lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;input
        type="email"
        id="email"
        name="email"
        required
        autocomplete="email"
        placeholder="john@example.com"
        aria-describedby="email-msg"
      &gt;
      &lt;output id="email-msg" for="email" aria-live="polite"&gt;
        We'll never share your email with anyone else.
      &lt;/output&gt;
    &lt;/form-field&gt;

    &lt;!-- Select dropdown --&gt;
    &lt;form-field&gt;
      &lt;label for="subject"&gt;Subject&lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;select id="subject" name="subject" required&gt;
        &lt;option value=""&gt;Select a topic...&lt;/option&gt;
        &lt;option value="general"&gt;General Inquiry&lt;/option&gt;
        &lt;option value="support"&gt;Technical Support&lt;/option&gt;
        &lt;option value="sales"&gt;Sales Question&lt;/option&gt;
        &lt;option value="feedback"&gt;Feedback&lt;/option&gt;
      &lt;/select&gt;
    &lt;/form-field&gt;

    &lt;!-- Textarea with minlength --&gt;
    &lt;form-field&gt;
      &lt;label for="message"&gt;Message&lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;textarea
        id="message"
        name="message"
        rows="5"
        required
        minlength="20"
        placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind..."
        aria-describedby="message-msg"
      &gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
      &lt;output id="message-msg" for="message" aria-live="polite"&gt;
        Minimum 20 characters.
      &lt;/output&gt;
    &lt;/form-field&gt;

    &lt;!-- Checkbox --&gt;
    &lt;form-field&gt;
      &lt;label&gt;
        &lt;input type="checkbox" name="newsletter" value="yes"&gt;
        Subscribe to our newsletter
      &lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;/form-field&gt;

    &lt;!-- Radio group --&gt;
    &lt;fieldset&gt;
      &lt;legend&gt;Preferred contact method&lt;/legend&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-layout-gap="xs"&gt;
        &lt;label&gt;
          &lt;input type="radio" name="contact-method" value="email" checked&gt;
          Email
        &lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;label&gt;
          &lt;input type="radio" name="contact-method" value="phone"&gt;
          Phone
        &lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
    &lt;/fieldset&gt;

    &lt;!-- Form actions --&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-layout-justify="flex-end" data-layout-gap="m"&gt;
      &lt;button type="reset" class="secondary"&gt;Reset&lt;/button&gt;
      &lt;button type="submit"&gt;Send Message&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Field Types</h2>

    <h3>Text Input</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Standard text input with label, placeholder, and helper text.</p>
    </layout-text>
    <code-block language="html" label="Text input">&lt;form-field&gt;
  &lt;label for="name"&gt;Full Name&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" id="name" name="name" required aria-describedby="name-msg"&gt;
  &lt;output id="name-msg" for="name" aria-live="polite"&gt;Helper text goes here.&lt;/output&gt;
&lt;/form-field&gt;</code-block>

    <h3>Select Dropdown</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Native select with placeholder option.</p>
    </layout-text>
    <code-block language="html" label="Select">&lt;form-field&gt;
  &lt;label for="subject"&gt;Subject&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select id="subject" name="subject" required&gt;
    &lt;option value=""&gt;Select a topic...&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="general"&gt;General Inquiry&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
&lt;/form-field&gt;</code-block>

    <h3>Checkbox</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Checkbox with label wrapping the input.</p>
    </layout-text>
    <code-block language="html" label="Checkbox">&lt;form-field&gt;
  &lt;label&gt;
    &lt;input type="checkbox" name="newsletter" value="yes"&gt;
    Subscribe to our newsletter
  &lt;/label&gt;
&lt;/form-field&gt;</code-block>

    <h3>Radio Group</h3>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Radio buttons grouped in a fieldset with legend.</p>
    </layout-text>
    <code-block language="html" label="Radio group">&lt;fieldset&gt;
  &lt;legend&gt;Preferred contact method&lt;/legend&gt;
  &lt;layout-stack data-layout-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;label&gt;
      &lt;input type="radio" name="contact-method" value="email" checked&gt;
      Email
    &lt;/label&gt;
    &lt;label&gt;
      &lt;input type="radio" name="contact-method" value="phone"&gt;
      Phone
    &lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
&lt;/fieldset&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Usage Notes</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Labels:</strong> Every input must have an associated label with matching <code>for</code>/<code>id</code> attributes</li>
        <li><strong>Autocomplete:</strong> Use appropriate <code>autocomplete</code> values to help browsers autofill</li>
        <li><strong>Validation:</strong> Use native attributes like <code>required</code>, <code>minlength</code>, <code>pattern</code>, and <code>type</code></li>
        <li><strong>Helper text:</strong> Use <code>&lt;output&gt;</code> with <code>aria-describedby</code> and <code>aria-live="polite"</code> for accessible hints</li>
        <li><strong>Grouping:</strong> Use <code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;legend&gt;</code> for radio/checkbox groups</li>
        <li><strong>Actions:</strong> Place submit/reset buttons at the end, typically right-aligned</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

